desc_short	-----								Play as 3 completely different classes. Fighter: Copy enemy attacks. Survivor: Dare to put yourself into danger. Trickster: Balance risk and power. Master the game via step-by-step missions, then show off the hardcore gamer within you with your perfected high-scores and excellent completion times.							
developer									Adventurous Productions								
